{"word":"G4812 - συλαγωγέω - sylagōgéō - soo-lag-ogue-eh'-o - Spoil","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συλαγωγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sylagōgéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soo-lag-ogue-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spoil</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொள்ளை கொண்டுபோ"},{"paragraph":"to carry off booty"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G4813 - συλάω - syláō - soo-lah'-o/4813\">G4813</a> and (the reduplicated form of) <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to <i>lead</i> away as <i>booty</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>seduce:</i> - spoil.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}